Product Description

Discover the face wash you'll love!

Our rich, creamy Hydrating Facial Cleanser activates with water, lightly-foaming to gently wash away excess oils & impurities, leaving skin supple, hydrated, & refreshed.

Our natural face wash is sulfate-free and lightly-lathers for a gentle yet deep clean to remove dirt, excess oil, & makeup, without stripping skin’s natural, beneficial oils. Skin is left feeling soft & supple, never tight or dry.

Gentle enough for daily use, this moisture-rich, non-drying face wash is freshly-made in small batches with deeply-hydrating Aloe Vera, skin-smoothing Avocado Fruit Extract, moisture-restoring Botanical Glycerol, & antioxidant-protective Essential Oil of Sage.

Vitamin-rich formula visibly smooths & renews, revealing healthier-looking skin. Potent antioxidants protect from free radicals, detoxifying & protecting skin from daily environmental stressors.

The subtle, natural aroma of sage calms the senses, & the luxurious-lather relaxes, transforming facial cleansing into a spa-like experience.

The non-irritating, pH-Optimized formula is gentle enough for morning & nightly use. Perfect for all skin types, both men & women.

Freshly-made in the USA for superior quality you can trust, with clean, organic, natural, & vegan ingredients.

Our Hand-Crafted formula is ultra-concentrated in a 118ml | 4 fl oz bottle. With just a small pump of cleanser, you’ll reveal skin that’s healthier-looking, supple, hydrated, & refreshed.

100% Money-Back Promise - Discover why men & women across the country are making the switch to Ktchn Apothecary! Enjoy your Fresh-Made Skincare for a full 90 days & if you don’t love it & reveal more healthier-looking skin, you'll get your money-back. Naturally.

OUR STORY

It all started with a dog named George.

Ever read what’s in your skincare? Don’t worry. Until a few years ago, I hadn’t either. Then one morning after applying a popular face moisturizer, my dog George jumped up and licked my face. For the first time, I wondered, ”What’s in this stuff…will George be okay?” So I read the ingredients and instead of high-performing, skin-nourishing natural ingredients, it was filled with unpronounceable chemicals.

Why? Other skincare is formulated to sit on a warehouse shelf for 2-5 Years before making its way to your home, so the formula is cluttered with Harsh Chemical Preservatives & Synthetics (like Plastic).

I got to thinking, if skincare was freshly-made, there’d be no shelf-life chemical clutter & more skin-nourishing ingredients at peak freshness to reveal healthier-looking skin.

Ktchn Apothecary Fresh-Made Skincare was born. And it all started with a dog named George.

-Kevin & George

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
